data.description: Welcome to this sprawling Grosse Ile ranch home in a quiet neighborhood not far from the water! The home has volumes of natural light in the living, dining and kitchen areas. Kitchen is open to family and dining room with step down to the living room.  Living and family room offer a shared natural fireplace. Two full baths, one with double sinks. Four large bedrooms with great closet space and all on almost half an acre!  Shed in backyard as well as a play place for the kids. Hot tub and covered patio in the back. Combination of furnace and heat pump make this home very efficient!  Stove is the only appliance staying in the home. Trampoline, TV's and TV mounts are excluded. Square footage believed to be accurate, but not guaranteed.  Buyers agent to verify all information.
